data.description:
2.625% Assumable VA Loan Available to those who qualify! 
Welcome to this move-in ready, 2020 built home, in the sought-after community of Wilford Preserve.  This stunning residence boasts 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a versatile flex room, perfect for an office, gym, or playroom, ensuring ample space for all your needs. The large primary suite features a serene soaker tub, large walk-in closet, and bay windows with a water view. Revel in the elegant tile flooring that flows throughout, guiding you through each thoughtfully designed space. The culinary enthusiast will adore the kitchen, equipped with a natural gas stove, built-in oven, and large island. Wilford Preserve features a plethora of amenities including a sparkling swimming pool, welcoming clubhouse, dog park, athletic fields, and a lively playground. Plus, with shopping centers and a range of restaurants just a 10-minute drive away, everything you need is within easy reach. Don't miss this chance to call this haven your home.
